kpi.name: M5001C30

kpi_info.title: BTS CHANNEL ELEMENT HSPA UTILIZATION IN UL - CLASS 4
kpi_info.use: The counter shows how many utilization rate samples have been detected within the (>60 - 80)% class per uplink direction. Each utilization rate sample calculates the number of CEs in use in HSPA divided by the number of all available (licensed) channel elements. UPDATED:The counter is incremented when the sample of the utilization rate is within (>60 - 80)% class.
